Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.81,0:00:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.32,0:00:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞絲娜 之後就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.74,0:00:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要衝動
